{"tid":1715062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國手足同我入黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:06:15.000Z","uid":338198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a927d6fac022e70cf459fd4cb383ca02e5c01d","tid":1715062,"uid":338198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"雖然我哋身處外國，但唔好以為自已咩都做唔到。唔好俾藉口自己，最基本要做到呢三樣嘢：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.英文文宣</span></span><br />\n香港嘅手足已經做得夠多中文文宣、尋人post等等。如果你嘅社交圈子有外國朋友，share多啲英文文宣。要令外國知道香港嘅嘢，你打中文係<span style=\"color: red;\">無撚用</span>。仲要捉住啲核彈黎報，愈多人知愈好。<br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅network你唔用盡，咁近嘅人可以講你唔講，條國際線可能就差你一個。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.去示威去靜坐簽petitions</span></span><br />\n好多國際大城市嘅大學都會有關係組，多啲留意佢哋嘅活動，幫手痴文宣，幫手叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n有搞香港club嘅試下搞關於香港示威嘅活動，唔需要好激烈，但起碼引起討論空間，等多啲人關心。可以搞movie screening，panel discussion，debate等等，有機會嘅叫埋當地媒體黎拍攝，好多都樂意採訪香港嘅聲音。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.捐錢</span></span><br />\n好多機構都可以透過PayPal或上網捐錢，唔需要香港銀行戶口。<br />\n<br />\n唔該自己上網check下，捐到就捐，每個人捐一蚊都幫到好多。人哋為你搏命為你擋子彈，你食少兩餐all you can eat捐錢都唔肯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海外手足都可以做多好多嘢，每個人行多一步，香港人就距離抗爭成功近一步。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 反抗</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">留翻條命睇黑警清算</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">約定煲底相見</span></span><br />\n<br />\nP牌幫手推唔該"},{"pid":"fa181cab66ede365690b06d8e41662fdace1747b","tid":1715062,"uid":338198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e9002881d6fdc277ed647de7f8927843df026f3","tid":1715062,"uid":338198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09ea1536911fd6b2f50e791f00458b5029e37011","tid":1715062,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙:bangbang::bangbang:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=b77e5181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=3f611c4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&h=6fdcee86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Cotton 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sentomcotton/status/1194354865432092673?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsentomcotton%2Fstatus%2F1194354865432092673%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=d234bd44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsentomcotton%2Fstatus%2F1194354865432092673%3Fs%3D21&h=ac800806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sentomcotton/status/1194354865432092673?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n!！眾議院多數黨領袖關注大學受襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LeaderHoyer/status/1194322000870854656?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeaderHoyer%2Fstatus%2F1194322000870854656%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=0293d7ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeaderHoyer%2Fstatus%2F1194322000870854656%3Fs%3D19&h=85f330df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LeaderHoyer/status/1194322000870854656?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter組會keep住更新</span><br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=ca09ab93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\nadmin會持續更新任務名單"},{"pid":"3fe59e4c01127ec55693b8a0382f654ad7bd9d5d","tid":1715062,"uid":338198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}